---
title: Char-Broiled BBQ Chicken with Summery Potato & Green Bean Salad
description: Nothing says summer like barbecue! That’s why we’re kicking of the season with one of our favorite summertime dishes: barbecue chicken and potato salad! We’re dressing this potato salad up with fresh basil and crisp green beans. If you have a grill it is great to use for this recipe instead of the broiler.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/char-broiled-bbq-chicken-38299efe.jpg
